# Environment Setup

## Objective

To establish a structured and scalable lab environment for practical learning, experimentation, and project-based development.

---

## Hardware Setup

- Primary Device: Windows 11 Laptop  
- Secondary Device: MacBook (backup system)  
- External SSD used as centralized lab storage  

